goal.ch:
1. 本課程以激發學生創意潛能與創業構想，實踐創新創業之理想為目的。
2. 本課程定位為創意與創業學分學程第一門課程，為此學程必修課程。
goal.en:
1. The objective of this course encourages innovation potential and entrepreneurship implementation.
2. This course is the first and required course of CAE program.

outline.ch: 本課程將開設一系列創意與創業相關講座，透過邀請全方位與多元創意創業專家之演講分享其豐富經驗，及小組討論之激盪，引領學生啟發自我的創意與創業潛力。
outline.en: This course invites experts/startup from multidisciplinary fields to share their experience and the students shall be grouped to develop their start-up business proposals and present it in the class.

gradMethod.ch:
1. 出席：20％
2. 心得報告：20％
3. 創業報告：60％ (BP口頭報告30％，Demo Day口頭報告20％，期末書面報告10％)
gradMethod.en:
Attendance: 20％
Study reports: 20％
Business proposal: 60％ (business plan presentation 30％, demo day presentation 20％, final report: 10％)

flexDiscription.ch: 第17、18週規畫創業報告自主討論與撰寫
flexDiscription.en: Weeks 17 and 18 are allocated for final report discussion and writing.
